cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine translation, which are typically categorized under cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of neural models, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which falls under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
